metadata.description:
Continuing my exploration in hues and shapes that light up the digital screen. Not every color in the spectrum reacts as emotively with digital backlight as those I search for. Hours of subtle shifts and layering techniques result in the final COLOR PIECES I share. These are high resolution and very printable. Please inquire about physical prints.
